		"duration": 459000000,
		"name": {
			"en": "Neoproterozoic",
			"fr": "Néoprotérozoïque"
		},
		"description": {
			"en": "Breakup of Rodinia supercontinent. Multiple global glaciations including Snowball Earth events. Emergence of complex multicellular life including the Ediacaran biota. Precursor to the Cambrian explosion.",
			"fr": "Fragmentation du supercontinent Rodinia. Multiples glaciations globales incluant les événements Terre boule de neige. Émergence de vie multicellulaire complexe incluant la biote de l'Édiacarien. Précurseur de l'explosion cambrienne."
		},
		"color": "#0369A1",
		"image": null
	},
	{
