		"duration": 50870000,
		"name": {
			"en": "Triassic",
			"fr": "Trias"
		},
		"description": {
			"en": "The opening period of the Mesozoic, when life slowly recovered after the devastating Permian extinction. Early dinosaurs and mammals both appeared, while the supercontinent Pangea remained largely intact.",
			"fr": "Période d'ouverture du Mésozoïque, durant laquelle la vie reprend lentement après la dévastatrice extinction permienne. Les premiers dinosaures et mammifères apparaissent, tandis que le supercontinent Pangée reste largement intact."
		},
		"color": "#78350F",
		"image": null
	},
	{
